onnection:<\/th><td>ANSI B16.5(Raised Flanged), ANSI B16.25(Butt Weld)<\/td><\/tr><\/tbody><\/table><p>\u00a0<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-33ecdf4 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"33ecdf4\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-587df1a e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"587df1a\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1c8d18e e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"1c8d18e\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e198014 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"e198014\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" width=\"700\" height=\"700\" src=\"https:\/\/Navjivanvalves.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/high-performance-butterfly-valve.jpg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-2481\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/Navjivanvalves.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/high-performance-butterfly-valve.jpg 700w, https:\/\/Navjivanvalves.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/high-performance-butterfly-valve-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/Navjivanvalves.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/high-performance-butterfly-valve-150x150.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-7574eb1 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"7574eb1\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-20d5b76 animated-slow elementor-invisible elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"20d5b76\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_animation&quot;:&quot;fadeInUp&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Navjivan's Butterfly Valves<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-db11f31 animated-slow elementor-invisible elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"db11f31\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_animation&quot;:&quot;fadeInUp&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">High Performance Butterfly Valves\n<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-519f3d5 elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget-mobile__width-inherit elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"519f3d5\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>High-performance butterfly valves (HPBV) are a specialized type of butterfly valve designed to withstand demanding conditions, including high pressures, high temperatures, and severe service applications.<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><p><strong>Design and Construction:<\/strong><\/p><p>\u2022 High-performance butterfly valves are available in various designs, including concentric, double offset, and triple offset configurations. Each design offers different levels of performance, with triple offset designs providing the highest level of performance and sealing integrity.<\/p><p>\u2022 High-performance butterfly valves feature robust construction with heavy-duty materials and advanced design features to ensure reliable performance in challenging environments.<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><p><strong>Materials of Construction:<\/strong><\/p><p>\u2022 High-performance butterfly valves are typically made from high-quality materials such as stainless steel, carbon steel, alloy steel, or exotic alloys, depending on the application requirements.<\/p><p>\u2022 The choice of material depends on factors such as the fluid being handled, temperature, pressure, corrosion resistance requirements, and compatibility with other system components.<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><p><strong>Applications:<\/strong><\/p><p>\u2022 High-performance butterfly valves are used in a wide range of industries and applications where reliable performance and tight shut-off are essential.<\/p><p>\u2022 They are commonly installed in power plants, chemical processing plants, oil and gas refineries, petrochemical facilities, HVAC systems, and water treatment plants, among others.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ee23505 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"ee23505\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-6750c9a e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"6750c9a\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e14eded e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"e14eded\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-8c1b2a1 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"8c1b2a1\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" width=\"700\" height=\"700\" src=\"https:\/\/Navjivanvalves.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/double-flanged-butterfly-valves.jpg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-2483\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/Navjivanvalves.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/double-flanged-butterfly-valves.jpg 700w, https:\/\/Navjivanvalves.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/double-flanged-butterfly-valves-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/Navjivanvalves.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/double-flanged-butterfly-valves-150x150.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-b13889b e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"b13889b\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d4fb5dd animated-slow elementor-invisible elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"d4fb5dd\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_animation&quot;:&quot;fadeInUp&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Navjivan's Butterfly Valves<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-882e09d animated-slow elementor-invisible elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"882e09d\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_animation&quot;:&quot;fadeInUp&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Double Flanged Butterfly Valves<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-29d724e elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget-mobile__width-inherit elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"29d724e\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Double flanged butterfly valves are a specific type of butterfly valve characterized by having flanges on both ends of the valve body.<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><p><strong>Design and Construction:<\/strong><\/p><p>\u2022 Double flanged butterfly valves feature a disc (or butterfly) mounted on a shaft in the center of the valve body.<\/p><p>\u2022 The valve body is designed with flanges on both the upstream and downstream ends, allowing for easy installation between flanged pipe connections.<\/p><p>\u2022 The disc is positioned perpendicular to the flow when the valve is closed and parallel to the flow when the valve is fully open.<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><p><strong>Materials of Construction:<\/strong><\/p><p>\u2022 Double flanged butterfly valves are available in a variety of materials to suit different application requirements, including carbon steel, stainless steel, cast iron, ductile iron, PVC (polyvinyl chloride), CPVC (chlorinated polyvinyl chloride), and other alloys.<\/p><p>\u2022 The choice of material depends on factors such as the fluid being handled, temperature, pressure, corrosion resistance requirements, and compatibility with other system components.<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><p><strong>Applications:<\/strong><\/p><p>\u2022 Double flanged butterfly valves are used in a wide range of industries and applications where reliable flow control and tight shut-off are required.<\/p><p>\u2022 They are commonly installed in water and wastewater systems, HVAC systems, chemical processing plants, power generation facilities, and other fluid handling systems.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e645cf7 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"e645cf7\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-b1433b5 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"b1433b5\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a3278fe e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"a3278fe\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-f45833c elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"f45833c\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"700\" height=\"700\" src=\"https:\/\/Navjivanvalves.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/wafer-lugged-butterfly-valves-1.jpg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-2173\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/Navjivanvalves.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/wafer-lugged-butterfly-valves-1.jpg 700w, https:\/\/Navjivanvalves.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/wafer-lugged-butterfly-valves-1-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/Navjivanvalves.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/wafer-lugged-butterfly-valves-1-150x150.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-66eae66 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"66eae66\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a29dc46 animated-slow elementor-invisible elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"a29dc46\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_animation&quot;:&quot;fadeInUp&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Navjivan's Butterfly Valves<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2134d5c animated-slow elementor-invisible elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"2134d5c\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_animation&quot;:&quot;fadeInUp&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Wafer Lugged Butterfly Valves<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-890b1a1 elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget-mobile__width-inherit elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"890b1a1\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-md-8\"><p>Wafer lugged butterfly valves are a specific type of butterfly valve designed with lugs or ears on the valve body to facilitate installation and ensure proper alignment within a piping system.<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><p><strong>Design and Construction:<\/strong><\/p><p>\u2022 Wafer lugged butterfly valves feature a disc (or butterfly) mounted on a shaft in the center of the valve body.<\/p><p>\u2022 The valve body is designed with lugs or ears on the outer circumference, which allow the valve to be secured between two flanges using bolts and nuts\/li&gt;<\/p><p>\u2022 The lugs provide additional support and stability, ensuring proper alignment and preventing movement or rotation of the valve within the pipeline.<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><p><strong>Materials of Construction:<\/strong><\/p><p>\u2022 Wafer lugged butterfly valves are available in a variety of materials to suit different application requirements, including carbon steel, stainless steel, cast iron, ductile iron, PVC (polyvinyl chloride), CPVC (chlorinated polyvinyl chloride), and other alloys.<\/p><p>\u2022 The choice of material depends on factors such as the fluid being handled, temperature, pressure, corrosion resistance requirements, and compatibility with other system components.<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><p><strong>Applications:<\/strong><\/p><p>\u2022 Wafer lugged butterfly valves are used in a wide range of industries and applications where reliable flow control and tight shut-off are required.<\/p><p>\u2022 They are commonly installed in water and wastewater systems, HVAC systems, chemical processing plants, power generation facilities, and other fluid handling systems.<\/p><\/div><div class=\"col-md-4\">\u00a0<\/div>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-37c8f3b e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"37c8f3b\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-731015c e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"731015c\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-62b2e44 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"62b2e44\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-0b4d7a3 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"0b4d7a3\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"700\" height=\"700\" src=\"https:\/\/Navjivanvalves.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/wafer-butterfly-valves.jpg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-2484\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/Navjivanvalves.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/wafer-butterfly-valves.jpg 700w, https:\/\/Navjivanvalves.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/wafer-butterfly-valves-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/Navjivanvalves.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/wafer-butterfly-valves-150x150.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-90c4c7f e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"90c4c7f\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1df2cf0 animated-slow elementor-invisible elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"1df2cf0\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_animation&quot;:&quot;fadeInUp&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Navjivan's Butterfly Valves<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3906dd6 animated-slow elementor-invisible elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"3906dd6\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_animation&quot;:&quot;fadeInUp&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Wafer Butterfly Valves<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-f053f3a elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget-mobile__width-inherit elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"f053f3a\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Wafer butterfly valves are a type of butterfly valve designed to fit between two flanges in a pipeline without the need for additional support or mounting brackets.<\/p><p><br><\/p>\n<p><strong>Design and Construction:<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>Wafer butterfly valves consist of a circular disc (or butterfly) mounted on a shaft in the center of the valve body.<\/p>\n<p>The valve body is designed with lugs or ears on the outer circumference, which allow the valve to be sandwiched between two flanges using bolts and nuts.<\/p>\n<p>This design eliminates the need for flange mounting brackets, making installation simpler and more cost-effective.<\/p>\n<p><strong><br><\/strong><\/p><p><strong>Applications:<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>Wafer butterfly valves are commonly used in industries where space and cost considerations are important factors, such as HVAC systems, water and wastewater treatment plants, chemical processing plants, and food and beverage processing facilities.<\/p>\n<p>They are suitable for handling a wide range of fluids, including water, air, gases, and light slurries.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-5d99593 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"5d99593\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-346e6ec animated-slow elementor-widget-mobile__width-inherit elementor-invisible elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"346e6ec\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_animation&quot;:&quot;fadeInUp&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Our Trusted Brands<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-f4074f3 animated-slow elementor-widget-mobile__width-inherit elementor-invisible elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"f4074f3\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_animation&quot;:&quot;fadeInUp&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Available Brands<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-99f1bcb elementor-widget__width-initia